<br>
I hate the whole need before greed thing. It assumes peeps are honest. First thing a dishonest person does is drop off lore item on a mule when going to Seb. Than they can roll on everything, they appear to need the item too. Like door locks.....Nb4G only keeps the honest people out.<br>
<br>
Also, my need for gear is the same for yours. This is not a socialist driven game. I can sell that RBG or whatever and buy something really sharp for my Shaman that he really &quot;needs&quot; ie. Lodzial Shield.<br>
<br>
Guild groups are different, they should always be decided on utility IMO. But in pick up groups.....I wouldno't know those people if I hit them with my car. Makes no difference to me what they need.<br>
<br>
